          "text": " to "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ],
          "text": "severe respiratory issues"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ". Understanding the causes and finding effective solutions can help you enjoy life with your beloved pets."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
